STORY

Tyrone is a Fire Sang’gre from the kingdom of Hathoria who dreams of 
becoming known throughout Encantadia. He strives to grow strong to protect his people.
When Joygen, one of Hathoria’s greatest protectors, vanished during the ritual,
Tyrone was shocked and saddened, believing it was no accident. Inspired by his admiration
for Joygen, he was chosen by the Brilyante of Apoy. Though the fire weakened after the ritual,
Tyrone vowed to restore its strength and uncover the truth, embarking on a journey that would
test his courage and heart.


